    "# 第15章: アクセス修飾子（解答集）\n",
    "\n",
    "## 学習目標\n",
    "- アクセス修飾子の種類と役割を理解する\n",
    "- public, private, protectedの使い分けができる\n",
    "- カプセル化の概念を理解する\n",
    "- ゲッター/セッターを実装できる"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## 問題1の解答: カプセル化とアクセス制御"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "**解説**:\n",
    "この問題ではカプセル化の基本を理解します。すべてのプロパティをprivateにし、外部からの操作をメソッド経由でしかできないようにします。\n",
    "\n",
    "- readonlyプロパティはPHP 8.1以降の機能です\n",
    "- 預金・引き出しの際に金額の妥当性をチェックします\n",
    "- 口座番号は変更不可能なreadonlyプロパティにします"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "<language>php</language><?php\n",
    "\n",
    "class BankAccount {\n",
    "    // プロパティはすべてprivateにして外部から直接操作できないようにする\n",
    "    private string $ownerName;\n",
    "    private int $balance = 0;\n",
    "    private string $accountType;\n",
    "    readonly string $accountNumber;\n",
    "    \n",
    "    public function __construct(string $accountNumber, string $ownerName, string $accountType) {\n",
    "        $this->accountNumber = $accountNumber;\n",
    "        $this->setOwnerName($ownerName);\n",
    "        $this->accountType = $accountType;\n",
    "    }\n",
    "    \n",
    "    // 預金メソッド\n",
    "    public function deposit(int $amount): void {\n",
    "        if ($amount > 0) {\n",
    "            $this->balance += $amount;\n",
    "            echo \"{$amount}円を預金しました\\n\";\n",
    "        } else {\n",
    "            echo \"預金金額は0より大きい必要があります\\n\";\n",
    "        }\n",
    "    }\n",
    "    \n",
    "    // 引き出しメソッド\n",
    "    public function withdraw(int $amount): bool {\n",
    "        if ($amount > 0 && $this->balance >= $amount) {\n",
    "            $this->balance -= $amount;\n",
    "            echo \"{$amount}円を引き出しました\\n\";\n",
    "            return true;\n",
    "        } else {\n",
    "            echo \"残高不足または不正な金額です\\n\";\n",
    "            return false;\n",
    "        }\n",
    "    }\n",
    "    \n",
    "    // ゲッター：残高を取得\n",
    "    public function getBalance(): int {\n",
    "        return $this->balance;\n",
    "    }\n",
    "    \n",
    "    // ゲッター：口座番号を取得\n",
    "    public function getAccountNumber(): string {\n",
    "        return $this->accountNumber;\n",
    "    }\n",
    "    \n",
    "    // セッター：名前を変更（バリデーション付き）\n",
    "    public function setOwnerName(string $newName): void {\n",
    "        if (empty(trim($newName))) {\n",
    "            throw new InvalidArgumentException('名前は必須です');\n",
    "        }\n",
    "        $this->ownerName = $newName;\n",
    "    }\n",
    "    \n",
    "    // 口座情報を表示\n",
    "    public function displayAccountInfo(): void {\n",
    "        echo \"【口座情報】\\n\";\n",
    "        echo \"口座番号: {$this->accountNumber}\\n\";\n",
    "        echo \"名義人: {$this->ownerName}\\n\";\n",
    "        echo \"口座種別: {$this->accountType}\\n\";\n",
    "        echo \"残高: {$this->balance}円\\n\";\n",
    "    }\n",
    "}\n",
    "\n",
    "// 使用例\n",
    "$account = new BankAccount('12345678', '山田太郎', '普通');\n",
    "$account->displayAccountInfo();\n",
    "\n",
    "echo \"\\n【預金と引き出し】\\n\";\n",
    "$account->deposit(10000);\n",
    "$account->withdraw(3000);\n",
    "echo \"現在の残高: {$account->getBalance()}円\\n\";\n",
    "\n",
    "// セッターで名前変更\n",
    "$account->setOwnerName('山田花子');\n",
    "$account->displayAccountInfo();\n",
    "\n",
    "// readonlyプロパティは変更できない（エラーになる）\n",
    "// $account->accountNumber = '87654321'; // Fatal error\n",
    "\n",
    "?>"
   ]
  },
