    "\n",
    "## 問題2の解答: 継承とアクセス修飾子"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "**解説**:\n",
    "この問題では継承時のアクセス修飾子のルールを理解します。\n",
    "\n",
    "- publicプロパティは継承先でもアクセス可能\n",
    "- protectedプロパティは継承先でもprotectedとしてアクセス可能\n",
    "- privateプロパティは継承先から一切アクセス不可\n",
    "- protectedメソッドはオーバーライド可能"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "<language>php</language><?php\n",
    "\n",
    "class Animal {\n",
    "    public string $name;\n",
    "    protected int $age;\n",
    "    private string $healthStatus;\n",
    "    \n",
    "    public function __construct(string $name, int $age) {\n",
    "        $this->name = $name;\n",
    "        $this->age = $age;\n",
    "        $this->healthStatus = '健康';\n",
    "    }\n",
    "    \n",
    "    public function eat(): void {\n",
    "        echo \"{$this->name}は餌を食べます\\n\";\n",
    "    }\n",
    "    \n",
    "    protected function sleep(): void {\n",
    "        echo \"{$this->name}は眠ります\\n\";\n",
    "    }\n",
    "    \n",
    "    private function checkHealth(): void {\n",
    "        echo \"{$this->name}の健康状態: {$this->healthStatus}\\n\";\n",
    "    }\n",
    "    \n",
    "    // privateプロパティにアクセス用のpublicメソッド\n",
    "    public function getHealthStatus(): string {\n",
    "        return $this->healthStatus;\n",
    "    }\n",
    "    \n",
    "    public function setHealthStatus(string $status): void {\n",
    "        $this->healthStatus = $status;\n",
    "    }\n",
    "}\n",
    "\n",
 "// DogクラスがAnimalを継承\n",
 "class Dog extends Animal {\n",
    "    public function bark(): void {\n",
    "        echo \"{$this->name}はワンワンと鳴きます！\\n\";\n",
    "        // 継承したprotectedメソッドを呼び出し可能\n",
    "        $this->sleep();\n",
    "    }\n",
    "    \n",
    "    protected function sleep(): void {\n",
    "        echo \"{$this->name}は夜に眠ります\\n\";\n",
    "    }\n",
    "    \n",
    "    public function setAge(int $age): void {\n",
    "        // protectedプロパティにアクセス可能\n",
    "        $this->age = $age;\n",
    "        echo \"年齢を{$age}歳に設定しました\\n\";\n",
    "    }\n",
    "    \n",
    "    public function getAge(): int {\n",
    "        return $this->age;\n",
    "    }\n",
    "}\n",
    "\n",
 "class Cat extends Animal {\n",
    "    public function meow(): void {\n",
    "        echo \"{$this->name}はニャーと鳴きます！\\n\";\n",
    "        $this->sleep();\n",
    "    }\n",
    "    \n",
    "    public function scratch(): void {\n",
    "        echo \"{$this->name}をひっかきました！\\n\";\n",
    "    }\n",
    "}\n",
    "\n",
 "class Bird extends Animal {\n",
    "    public function fly(): void {\n",
    "        echo \"{$this->name}は空を飛びます！\\n\";\n",
    "    }\n",
    "    \n",
    "    public function chirp(): void {\n",
    "        echo \"{$this->name}はさえずります！\\n\";\n",
    "    }\n",
    "}\n",
    "\n",
 "// 使用例\n",
 "echo \"【動物たち】\\n\";\n",
 "$dog = new Dog('ポチ', 3);\n",
 "$cat = new Cat('ミケ', 2);\n",
 "$bird = new Bird('スズメ', 1);\n",
 "\n",
 "// publicプロパティは変更可能\n",
 "$dog->name = 'シロ';\n",
 "\n",
 "// 各動物のメソッド呼び出し\n",
 "$dog->eat();\n",
 "$dog->bark();\n",
 "echo \"犬の年齢: {$dog->getAge()}歳\\n\\n\";\n",
 "\n",
 "$cat->eat();\n",
 "$cat->meow();\n",
 "$cat->scratch();\n",
 "\n",
 "$bird->eat();\n",
 "$bird->fly();\n",
 "$bird->chirp();\n",
 "\n",
 "// healthStatusはprivateなので直接アクセスできない\n",
 "// echo $dog->healthStatus; // エラー\n",
 "echo \"犬の健康状態: {$dog->getHealthStatus()}\\n\";\n",
 "\n",
 "?>"
   ]
